# Vercel Web Analytics Configuration Report

## Summary
Vercel Web Analytics is **already fully configured** in this project. No changes were necessary.

## Current Configuration

### Package Installation
- **Package**: `@vercel/analytics` version `^2.0.1`
- **Location**: Listed in `dependencies` in `web/package.json`
- **Status**: ✅ Installed and up-to-date

### Implementation
- **File**: `web/app/layout.tsx`
- **Import**: `import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";`
- **Component**: `<Analytics />` component added at the end of the `<body>` tag
- **Framework**: Next.js App Router (correct implementation pattern per official docs)

### Verification Steps Completed
1. ✅ Fetched latest Vercel Web Analytics documentation from https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/quickstart
2. ✅ Verified package installation (`@vercel/analytics@2.0.1`)
