## Implementation Details

The Analytics component is correctly positioned in the root layout file (`web/app/layout.tsx`) following the official Vercel documentation guidelines for Next.js App Router applications:

```typescript
import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="en">
      <body>
        {/* ...other components... */}
        <Analytics />
      </body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

This implementation matches the exact pattern recommended in the Vercel documentation fetched from https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/quickstart for Next.js App Router projects.

